  //
  // invZ must be the inverse of the z returned by _projectiveECAdd(p1, p2).
  // It is computed off-chain to save gas.
  //
  // p1 and p2 must be distinct, because _projectiveECAdd doesn't handle
  // point doubling.
  function _affineECAdd(
    uint256[2] memory p1,
    uint256[2] memory p2,
    uint256 invZ
